# System Safeguards for Trendscope Testing

## Memory Limits
- Max RAM per test: 2GB
- Max test duration: 60 seconds
- No browser downloads during CI
- Use mocked responses where possible

## Testing Rules
1. Always use `timeout` command
2. Set `ulimit -v 2097152` (2GB virtual memory)
3. Prefer unit tests over integration tests
4. Skip live tests by default
5. Use `--collect-only` before running full suite
